### Environment
# Uses `rest-client.env.json` (workspace root) or `.vscode/rest-client.env.json`.
# Select environment via: `REST Client: Switch Environment` (e.g., "local").
# Default fallback (uncomment if your env isn’t picked up):
@employeeApiBase = http://localhost:5016

### Health check
GET {{employeeApiBase}}/api/employees/health
Accept: application/json

### Swagger UI
GET {{employeeApiBase}}/swagger
